{
  "stem": "1975.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "His name was Mek, M-E-K.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they pointed out that this Jew didn't turn in some of his valuables.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that's the reason why they hanged him publicly.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And-- and he was hanging for seven days, in-- in a-- in a very noticeable spot, so the people are going to understand that they mean business.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[BACKROUND NOISE] There was also a very interesting incident, which affected me personally.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And this was right when-- when they closed the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They called for 500 [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] intelligent people.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I don't mean 'intelligent' of saying being intelligent, but people who had-- educated people, I would say.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They need them-- they claim they need them for-- needed them for a very-- very special assignment.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And, of course, people start to run, because they felt that this must be-- and also, they promised that they are going to be-- their assignment is going to be very special.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They are going to have extra food, and they are going to have extra shelter.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So everybody start running to this place.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Myself, I was going with my-- with my aunt's brother, who was going with me.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And for some reason, he-- he got delayed for a little while.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And he was doing something in-- in-- inside the apartment.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And we came-- when we came, [BACKROUND NOISE] there were some people who were faster, apparently, than us.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And they told us, that's it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I mean, when they said, 500, they had, like, 503 people.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "That's it.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And many people have pushed themselves.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "They-- they wanted to be there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And can you believe this?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, the first 500 people that they took out and they shot them the next day, all of them.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They machine-gunned all those 500 people.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
